52#ifndef CREATE_H_
53#define CREATE_H_
54
55#include "types.h"
56#include "packet.h"
57#include "crypto.h"
58#include "errors.h"
59#include "keyring.h"
60#include "writer.h"
61#include "memory.h"
62
63/**
64 * \ingroup Create
65 * This struct contains the required information about how to write this stream
66 */
67struct pgp_output_t {
68 pgp_writer_t writer;
69 pgp_error_t *errors; /* error stack */
70};
71
72pgp_output_t *pgp_output_new(void);
73void pgp_output_delete(pgp_output_t *);
74
75int pgp_filewrite(const char *, const char *, const size_t, const unsigned);
76
77void pgp_build_pubkey(pgp_memory_t *, const pgp_pubkey_t *, unsigned);
78
79unsigned pgp_calc_sesskey_checksum(pgp_pk_sesskey_t *, uint8_t *);
80unsigned pgp_write_struct_userid(pgp_output_t *, const uint8_t *);
81unsigned pgp_write_ss_header(pgp_output_t *, unsigned, pgp_content_enum);
82unsigned pgp_write_struct_seckey(const pgp_seckey_t *,
83 const uint8_t *,
84 const size_t,
85 pgp_output_t *);
86unsigned pgp_write_one_pass_sig(pgp_output_t *,
87 const pgp_seckey_t *,
88 const pgp_hash_alg_t,
89 const pgp_sig_type_t);
90unsigned pgp_write_litdata(pgp_output_t *,
91 const uint8_t *,
92 const int,
93 const pgp_litdata_enum);
94pgp_pk_sesskey_t *pgp_create_pk_sesskey(const pgp_key_t *, const char *);
95unsigned pgp_write_pk_sesskey(pgp_output_t *, pgp_pk_sesskey_t *);
96unsigned pgp_write_xfer_pubkey(pgp_output_t *,
97 const pgp_key_t *, const unsigned);
98unsigned pgp_write_xfer_seckey(pgp_output_t *,
99 const pgp_key_t *,
100 const uint8_t *,
101 const size_t,
102 const unsigned);
103
104void pgp_fast_create_userid(uint8_t **, uint8_t *);
105unsigned pgp_write_userid(const uint8_t *, pgp_output_t *);
106void pgp_fast_create_rsa_pubkey(pgp_pubkey_t *, time_t, BIGNUM *, BIGNUM *);
107unsigned pgp_write_rsa_pubkey(time_t, const BIGNUM *, const BIGNUM *,
108 pgp_output_t *);
109void pgp_fast_create_rsa_seckey(pgp_seckey_t *, time_t, BIGNUM *,
110 BIGNUM *, BIGNUM *, BIGNUM *,
111 BIGNUM *, BIGNUM *);
112unsigned encode_m_buf(const uint8_t *, size_t, const pgp_pubkey_t *,
113 uint8_t *);
114unsigned pgp_fileread_litdata(const char *, const pgp_litdata_enum,
115 pgp_output_t *);
116unsigned pgp_write_symm_enc_data(const uint8_t *, const int,
117 pgp_output_t *);
118
119#endif /* CREATE_H_ */
